---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

---
<Layout title="vallees-connectees" >
    <div class="my-20 mx-10">
        <div class="my-3 text-center text-3xl">Atelier de culture numérique</div>
        <div class="my-2 text-center text-xl">18 novembre 2023 - médiathèque de Munster</div>
        <hr class="mt-10 mb-1"/>
        <hr class="mb-10"/>

        <div id="accordion-collapse" data-accordion="collapse">
            <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-1">
                <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right text-gray-500 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 rounded-t-xl focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-200 dark:focus:ring-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 gap-3" data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-1">
                    <span class="font-bold uppercase">Introduction</span>
                    <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
                        <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"/>
                    </svg>
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="accordion-collapse-body-1" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-1">
                <div class="p-5 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-900">
                    <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Si vous souhaitez en savoir plus sur notre association, n'hésitez pas à consulter notre  <a href="https://vallees-connectees.alsace" class="text-blue  hover:underline" target="_blank">site internet</a>.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-2">
                <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right text-gray-500 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-200 dark:focus:ring-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 gap-3" data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-2">
                    <span class="font-bold uppercase">Le framapad</span>
                    <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
                        <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"/>
                    </svg>
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="accordion-collapse-body-2" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-2">
                <div class="p-5 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                    <p class="mb-2 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                        Un framapad est un document texte collaboratif (comme un google document).
                        Nous nous l'utiliserons tout au long de l'atelier. Il est accessible <a href="https://mensuel.framapad.org/p/atelier-numerique-a4f1?lang=fr" class="text-blue" target="_blank">ici</a>.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-3">
                <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right text-gray-500 border border-gray-200 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-200 dark:focus:ring-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 gap-3" data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-3">
                    <span class="font-bold uppercase">Blind test</span>
                    <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
                        <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"/>
                    </svg>
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="accordion-collapse-body-3" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-3">
                <div class="p-5 border border-t-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                    <p class="mb-2 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                        Voici des liens vers les différents systèmes / ordinateurs mentionnés dans le blind test :
                    <div class="container mx-auto p-4">
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4">

                            <div class="border p-2 text-center">
                            <a href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Windows_XP" target="_blank" class="text-blue hover:underline">Son 1</a>
                        </div>
                            <div class="border p-2 text-center">
                                <a href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Windows_95" target="_blank" class="text-blue hover:underline">Son 2</a>
                            </div>

                            <div class="border p-2 text-center">
                                <a href="https://www.apple.com/fr/macos/sonoma/" target="_blank" class="text-blue hover:underline">Son 3</a>
                            </div>

                            <div class="border p-2 text-center">
                                <a href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Power_Macintosh" target="_blank" class="text-blue hover:underline">Son 4</a>
                            </div>

                            <div class="border p-2 text-center">
                                <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/fr-fr/windows/windows-11" target="_blank" class="text-blue hover:underline">Son 5</a>
                            </div>

                            <div class="border p-2 text-center">
                                <a href="https://www.ubuntu-fr.org/" target="_blank" class="text-blue hover:underline">Son 6</a>
                            </div>

                            <div class="border p-2 text-center">
                                <a href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Windows_Millennium_Edition" target="_blank" class="text-blue hover:underline">Son 7</a>
                            </div>

                            <div class="border p-2 text-center">
                                <a href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Windows_Vista" target="_blank" class="text-blue hover:underline">Son 8</a>
                            </div>

                            <div class="border p-2 text-center">
                                <a href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Macintosh_II" target="_blank" class="text-blue hover:underline">Son 9</a>
                            </div>

                            <div class="border p-2 text-center">
                                <a href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Windows_98" target="_blank" class="text-blue hover:underline">Son 10</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-4">
                <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right text-gray-500 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-200 dark:focus:ring-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 gap-3" data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-4">
                    <span class="font-bold uppercase">Les composants d'un ordinateur</span>
                    <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
                        <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"/>
                    </svg>
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="accordion-collapse-body-4" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-4">
                <div class="p-5 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                    <p class="mb-2 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                        Remplissez la zone de texte ci-dessous avec les composants d'un ordinateur :
                        <textarea class="w-full px-3 py-2 text-gray-700 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none" rows="4">
                            </textarea>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-5">
                <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right text-gray-500 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-200 dark:focus:ring-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 gap-3" data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-5">
                    <span class="font-bold uppercase">Dessin-cloud-coop</span>
                    <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
                        <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"/>
                    </svg>
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="accordion-collapse-body-5" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-5">
                <div class="p-5 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                    <p class="mb-2 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                    Les différentes icônes représentent :
                        - le pc personnel
                        - la box domestique
                        - deux pare-feux
                        - les cables sous-marins
                        - un data-center
                        - un serveur mail
                        - le chiffrement des données
                        - les données personnelles
                    </p>

                    <p class="mb-2 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                       Les liens ci-dessous sont intéressants, en lien avec le cloud (mais ne vous aideront
                        pas forcément pour le dessin) :
                        - <a href="https://www.submarinecablemap.com/" target="_blank" class="text-blue hover:underline">Carte des câbles sous-marins</a>
                        - <a href="https://www.datacentermap.com/cloud/g/france" target="_blank" class="text-blue hover:underline">La carte des fournisseurs de cloud</a>
                        - <a href="https://www.google.com/about/datacenters/efficiency/" target="_blank" class="text-blue hover:underline">Politique de google sur l'efficience énergétique des datacenter</a>
                    </p>

                </div>
            </div>

            <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-10">
                <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right text-gray-500 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-200 dark:focus:ring-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 gap-3" data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-10" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-10">
                    <span class="font-bold uppercase">Sécurité de bout en bout</span>
                    <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
                        <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"/>
                    </svg>
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="accordion-collapse-body-10" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-10">
                <div class="p-5 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                    <p class="mb-2 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                        Pour introduction, vous pouvez aller ici :
                        <a href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cryptographie_asym%C3%A9trique" target="_blank" class="text-blue hover:underline">Crypto asymétrique</a><br>
                        C'est parti pour l'envoi de message !
                    </p>
                    <p>
                    On voulait aussi vous parler des mails frauduleux. Vous savez, ceux qui vous demandent vos données personnelles ?
                        Alors pour en savoir plus, vous pouvez vous rendre ici :
                        <a href="https://www.cybermalveillance.gouv.fr/tous-nos-contenus/actualites/comment-reconnaitre-un-mail-de-phishing-ou-dhameconnage" target="_blank" class="text-blue hover:underline">Cybervigilance</a><br>

                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-6">
                <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right text-gray-500 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-200 dark:focus:ring-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 gap-3" data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-6" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-6">
                    <span class="font-bold uppercase">Stocker ses données</span>
                    <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
                        <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"/>
                    </svg>
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="accordion-collapse-body-6" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-6">
                <div class="p-5 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                    <div class="w-full p-5">
                        <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-6">
                            <div class="md:col-span-1">
                                <label for="storage-name" class="block text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">Nom du support de stockage</label>
                                <input type="text" id="storage-name" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none text-gray-700" />
                            </div>
                            <div class="md:col-span-1">
                                <label for="release-year" class="block text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">Année de sortie du support</label>
                                <input type="text" id="release-year" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none text-gray-700" />
                            </div>
                            <div class="md:col-span-1">
                                <label for="max-size" class="block text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">Taille maximale du support</label>
                                <input type="text" id="max-size" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none text-gray-700" />
                            </div>
                            <div class="md:col-span-1">
                                <label for="price" class="block text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">Prix</label>
                                <input type="text" id="price" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none text-gray-700" />
                            </div>
                            <div class="md:col-span-1">
                                <label for="advantages" class="block text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">Avantages</label>
                                <input type="text" id="advantages" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none text-gray-700" />
                            </div>
                            <div class="md:col-span-1">
                                <label for="disadvantages" class="block text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">Inconvénients</label>
                                <input type="text" id="disadvantages" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border rounded-lg focus:outline-none text-gray-700" />
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-7">
                <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right text-gray-500 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-200 dark:focus:ring-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 gap-3" data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-7" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-7">
                    <span class="font-bold uppercase">Le numérique ouvert</span>
                    <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
                        <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"/>
                    </svg>
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="accordion-collapse-body-7" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-7">
                <div class="p-5 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                    <p class="mb-2 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                        Voici les différents liens mentionnés dans l'article :<br>
                        <a href="https://data.gouv.fr" target="_blank" class="text-blue hover:underline">https://data.gouv.fr</a><br>
                        <a href="https://legifrance.gouv.fr" target="_blank" class="text-blue hover:underline">https://legifrance.gouv.fr</a><br>
                        <a href="https://www.geoportail.gouv.fr" target="_blank" class="text-blue hover:underline">https://geoportail.gouv.fr</a><br>
                        <a href="https://framalibre.org/" target="_blank" class="text-blue hover:underline">https://framalibre.org/</a><br>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-8">
                <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right text-gray-500 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-200 dark:focus:ring-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 gap-3" data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-8" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-8">
                    <span class="font-bold uppercase">L'enquête IP</span>
                    <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
                        <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"/>
                    </svg>
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="accordion-collapse-body-8" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-8">
                <div class="p-5 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                    <p class="mb-2 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                        Voici des indices (mais vous pouvez aussi demander à Google) :<br>
                        <a href="https://www.apnic.net/about-apnic/whois_search/your-ip/" target="_blank" class="text-blue hover:underline">APNIC</a><br>
                        <a href="https://www.arcep.fr/la-regulation/grands-dossiers-internet-et-numerique/lipv6/suivi-de-lepuisement-des-adresses-ipv4.html" target="_blank" class="text-blue hover:underline">ARCEP</a><br>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-9">
                <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium rtl:text-right text-gray-500 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-200 dark:focus:ring-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 gap-3" data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-9" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-9">
                    <span class="font-bold uppercase">Le juste prix... de CO2</span>
                    <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 10 6">
                        <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"/>
                    </svg>
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="accordion-collapse-body-9" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-9">
                <div class="p-5 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                    <p class="mb-2 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                        Saurez-vous trouver les chiffres manquants ? <br>
                        <a href="https://www.arcep.fr/la-regulation/grands-dossiers-thematiques-transverses/lempreinte-environnementale-du-numerique/etude-ademe-arcep-empreinte-environnemental-numerique-2020-2030-2050.html" target="_blank" class="text-blue hover:underline">Etude ADEME – Arcep sur l’empreinte environnementale du numérique en 2020, 2030 et 2050</a><br>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>